{"tid":168774,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"兵工廠邊翼:球隊已提與雲格續約 教授會做最好決定","createTime":"2017-03-23T18:24:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-24T06:21:35.000Z","uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0f39796afef1cd09dc82d5ca65c904e953e3c95a","tid":168774,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T18:24:57.000Z","msg":"香港時間3月24日，據英格蘭媒體《每日鏡報》報導，阿仙奴邊後衛蒙利爾在接受採訪時力撐雲格。蒙利爾表示阿仙奴球員和大多數球迷都支持雲格，相信雲格會做出對他和阿仙奴來說最好的決定。<br />\n<br />\n　　在此前的比賽中，阿仙奴球迷雇飛機拉橫幅要求教授下台，蒙利爾在接受採訪時稱球員在困難時期是教練的後盾：「最近阿仙奴在英超5輪輸了4場，歐冠盃也慘敗出局，這些負面情緒也會影響到球員以及球會。」<br />\n<br />\n　　蒙利爾稱：「希望雲格下台的只是部分球迷，大多數球迷還與雲格站在一起。關於他的未來，他有最後的話語權，他將決定是否繼續執教，因為球會已經提出續約合約，我相信他會做出對他和球會來說最好的決定。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/3/2017/03/24/3/39d2307dae1bcacf4330a0db58d94929.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F3%2F2017%2F03%2F24%2F3%2F39d2307dae1bcacf4330a0db58d94929.jpg&h=f8e7577d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雲加又嬴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4026bcb09aee9ad30bab0ef6e0cc345155645adf","tid":168774,"uid":21899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T18:28:37.000Z","msg":"就係教到落英冠都有得續約你吹咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d572c9d32b1365e86c88cdf3685d7b32726bff2","tid":168774,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T18:30:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>就係教到落英冠都有得續約你吹咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無限光環<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0da11ca5aeebacdf6d6607124dd0d07de8d5e9b","tid":168774,"uid":33653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T18:52:16.000Z","msg":"全地球迫害雲爺爺"},{"pid":"f39379caacdf043dabbce08bf8a9a99a89ebc58e","tid":168774,"uid":26389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T19:00:48.000Z","msg":"爺爺<img src